    <header>
      <h1 class="entry-title">Cartel Madras picks their all-time favorite songs for The 2020 Countdown</h1>
      <time class="published" datetime="2020-10-16T18:26:31-04:00">October 16th, 2020 | 6:26PM | </time>By <a href="https://thekey.xpn.org/author/jvettese/" rel="author" class="fn">John Vettese</a>
<!-- This was enclosing author name

<p class="byline author vcard"></p> 

-->
<!-- this was the featured category links -->
    </header>
    <div class="entry-content">    
      <div style='display:none;' class='shareaholic-canvas' data-app='share_buttons' data-title='Cartel Madras picks their all-time favorite songs for The 2020 Countdown' data-link='https://thekey.xpn.org/2020/10/16/cartel-madras-picks-their-all-time-favorite-songs-for-the-2020-countdown/' data-app-id-name='post_above_content'></div>
<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-256664" srcset="https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626.jpg 2000w, https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626-768x512.jpg 768w, https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626-620x413.jpg 620w, https://thekey.xpn.org/aatk/files/2018/09/Q47A2626-640x427.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption>Kendrick Lamar | photo by John Vettese for WXPN</figcaption></figure>



<p>For the fall of 2020, WXPN is once again <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://thekey.xpn.org/2020/08/17/xpn-2020-countdown-greatest-2020-songs-of-all-time/" target="_blank">asking its audience to help choose the 2,020 greatest songs of all time</a>. While the voting period is open, we’ve asked prominent Philadelphians and some of our favorite musicians to share their favorites to get us thinking about our lists. Today, we present an assortment of rap, pop, indie and more, chosen by Canadian hip-hop duo Cartel Madras for <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://thekey.xpn.org/search/the+2020+countdown" target="_blank">The 2020 Countdown</a>. Check it out below and cast your vote <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://xpn.org/music-artist/885-countdown/2020/vote" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>



<span id="more-298639"></span>
